<div>
  <p>
    The following packages are for macOS Sierra or higher.
  </p>
  <p>
    The processor(s) must support the SSE 4.2 instruction set
    (Intel Nehalem or better, AMD Bulldozer or better, etc.)
  </p>
  <p>
    We provide a single package containing the server and the client tools. For a
    standard server setup, download the <strong>Server</strong> package and
    install it using the package manager.
  </p>
  <p>
    As an alternative there is a <strong>Tar</strong> package containing the server and
    client tools, which can be unpacked in any location.
  </p>
  <hr/>
  <p><strong>DMG</strong> package</p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <a href="@DOWNLOAD_LINK@/MacOSX/@BUNDLE_NAME_SERVER@">Server @ARANGODB_VERSION@</a><br>
      (@BUNDLE_SIZE_SERVER@ MByte, SHA256 @BUNDLE_SHA256_SERVER@)
    </li>
  </ul>
  <p><strong>Tar</strong> package</p>
  <ul>
    <li>
      <a href="@DOWNLOAD_LINK@/MacOSX/@TARGZ_NAME_SERVER@">Server @ARANGODB_VERSION@</a><br>
      (@TARGZ_SIZE_SERVER@ MByte, SHA256 @TARGZ_SHA256_SERVER@)
    </li>
  </ul>
</div>
